{"cards":[{"lines":[{"type":"title","text":"Lack of resolution leads to art"}]},{"lines":[{"type":"title","text":"Grating spectroscope"}]}],"definitions":[],"secText":["  <b>Lesson:<\/b>  <b>    <br \/>  <\/b>1. Define <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='18' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='1' data-subsection='0'>resolving power<\/a>.<br \/>2. <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='18' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='1' data-subsection='1'>Apply<\/a> the concept of diffraction to resolving power.<br \/>3. Apply the concept of resolving power to <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='18' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='1' data-subsection='2'>principles of art<\/a>.<br \/>4. Apply the concept of resolving power to <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='18' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='2' data-subsection='0'>computer displays and pixels<\/a>.<br \/>5. Describe the interference pattern of <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='18' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='2' data-subsection='1'>diffraction gratings<\/a>.<br \/>6. Apply the concept of interference to <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='18' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='2' data-subsection='2'>CDs and DVDs<\/a>.<br \/>7. Apply the concept of diffraction gratings to a <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='18' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='2' data-subsection='3'>grating spectroscope<\/a>.<br \/>7. Define and calculate the minimum angle required for resolution using <a class='pjumpToTopic' href='javascript:void(0)' data-chap='18' data-topic='4' data-subtopic='3' data-subsection='0'>Rayleigh's criterion<\/a>.","  <b>Homework:<\/b>  <span class=\"KBInternalLink\"><a href=\"assign.html#OHW 18.05\">OHW 18.05<\/a><\/span>","  <b>Quick Review:<\/b>  <a class='pjumpToVideo' href='javascript:void(0)' data-video='true' data-vref='sum_resolution'>Resolving Power<\/a>"],"objNames